cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a convolution neural network based algorithm for diagnosing diabetic retinopathy and highlighting suspicious regions in retinal images. This involves image processing, computer vision, and machine learning techniques, which are all related to the computer science sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
